body:
There appears to be an issue on Windows when drawing text onto a scaled canvas:

```csharp
// scale
canvas.Scale (1, 2);

// paint
var paint = new SKPaint {
    TextSize = 50
};

// draw
canvas.DrawText ("Skia", 10, 60, paint);
```
![first](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1096616/24983859/31a18f46-1fea-11e7-9a6b-24b572c646ee.PNG)

But if we set antialiasing on:

```csharp
paint.IsAntialias = true;
```

![second](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1096616/24983860/3426f4cc-1fea-11e7-877a-3a187bfb609e.PNG)
